    <div class="summary">
        <h3><a href="/questions/47518/does-the-mysql-parameter-max-connections-apply-for-unix-socket-connections" class="question-hyperlink">Does the mysql parameter &ldquo;max_connections&rdquo; apply for unix socket connections?</a></h3>
        <div class="excerpt">
            The documentation does not specify if max_connections apply only to TCP connections. 

